@startuml
title Dynamic Resource Location Discovery

participant "Part Agent" as Part
participant "Crane Agent" as Crane
participant "Source Agent" as Source
participant "Process Agent" as Process

Part -> Crane : Transport product\nSource → Process

Crane -> Source : getLocation()
Source --> Crane : sourceX, sourceY

Crane -> Process : getLocation()
Process --> Crane : processX, processY

Crane -> Crane : Build movement sequence\nusing returned coordinates
Crane --> Part : Transport accepted

note over Crane
No hardcoded coordinate table.

Changing Process 1 and Process 2
locations does not require changes
to the Crane Agent.
end note

@enduml